text: Alf Olsen (4 November 1925 - 24 February 2001) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stavanger
